==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Greeting
<hw>Greet"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Expression of kindness or joy;
salutation at meeting; a compliment from one absent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Write to him . . . gentle adieus and <qex>greetings.</qex></q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Salutation; salute; compliment.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Greeve</ent>⟦br⟧
